{"tid":2282686,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"血友病16歲男生襲警罪成 還柙期間一度傷口發炎 今獲准保釋候社會服務令報告候判","createTime":"2020-11-12T04:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T08:23:36.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b6fc51d75b71c317f49b23c6926eb97c8c417a78","tid":2282686,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T04:34:17.000Z","msg":"網民去年11月發起「七區行街」行動，當晚有警員在柴灣追捕16歲男生時跌倒拗傷，事後指控是男生兩度推開他所致。男生早前經審訊後被裁定襲警罪成，原定還柙至今天判刑。庭上透露，男生自中一起患上血友病，案件裁決前剛完成手術，還柙期間傷口發炎，等了一天方獲治理。裁判官崔美霞明言，犯事者不會因年輕而僅「打手板」了事，惟考慮到被告身體狀況等因素，決定以人道理由再為他索閱社會服務令報告，亦批准已還柙兩周的被告保釋回家。<br />\n<br />\n辯方今進一步求情指，報告認為16歲被告基於健康問題，不適合入住勞教中心、更生中心或教導所。辯方又透露，被告患有血友病，案件裁決前剛完成手術，還柙期間傷口發炎，未能適時接受治理，待至隔日方可求醫。<br />\n<br />\n辯方今亦呈上男生就讀學校的副校長、社工及兩名班主任所寫求情信。社工在被告牽涉本案後跟進其情況，他撰信指師長對被告牽涉本案感到驚訝，認為他並非愛好衝突或暴力的人。被告涉案後沒有一蹶不振，更做兼職幫補家計。社工認為，被告遭還柙，身心已受折磨和打擊，如被判處拘禁式刑罰，被告的成長會留下不可磨滅的印記，亦會影響他應付公開試。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201112/D54PDNSYARAADFBU2GJOHZCDDE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201112%2FD54PDNSYARAADFBU2GJOHZCDDE%2F&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2AuyF8jviwHHlsaTD6zKFHFMM%3D&h=8fd533e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201112%2FD54PDNSYARAADFBU2GJOHZCDDE%2F&h=b7ece667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201112/D54PDNSYARAADFBU2GJOHZCDDE/</a>"},{"pid":"e1d48896276461952b42ab6cdc06bb3b015936e7","tid":2282686,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T04:40:12.000Z","msg":"藍屍： 用監獄無得醫病？<br />\n<br />\n個官都算係咁"},{"pid":"e37ae5fa9cba444b53402b94b93b4db5005d4fd5","tid":2282686,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1d48896276461952b42ab6cdc06bb3b015936e7","tid":2282686,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T04:40:12.000Z","msg":"藍屍： 用監獄無得醫病？<br />\n<br />\n個官都算係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T04:43:14.000Z","msg":"崔美霞 好似尚算正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb516e440504aef61c755ec0b57d857817ac111","tid":2282686,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T04:45:57.000Z","msg":"罪成+還押=狗官"},{"pid":"8397af915b6c1563acecac2890eda34226bfe0d5","tid":2282686,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T04:50:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b2719a12c875e710179ee7c853cd03ec3a86b6d","tid":2282686,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T05:37:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2fb085fa2e6afd2a3a1e223fc491df47106eedeb","tid":2282686,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T08:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b10e731cb08dd93d7d77bd3291f25049eaf1cf","tid":2282686,"uid":200070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1d48896276461952b42ab6cdc06bb3b015936e7","tid":2282686,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T04:40:12.000Z","msg":"藍屍： 用監獄無得醫病？<br />\n<br />\n個官都算係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T08:23:36.000Z","msg":"OMDB<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}